You start learning basic piano from a friend. (+skill points)
You fall while running and scrape your knee. (-health, -luck)
You feel pressure to be “better than others.” (-EQ, -luck)
You break an expensive toy and get scolded harshly. (-EQ, -loveReceiving)
A nanny drops you by accident, leaving a small scar. (-look, -health)